"{name} {peer_v} is too old for the AZT Collaboration service.\n"
"This build bundles client library {bundled}; the service requires "
"{required} or newer.\n"
"No newer {name} release is published yet. Check back later or "
"[ref=email][color=4ea1ff][u]send the developer an Email[/u][/color][/ref]."
